Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:24:00.52,DefaultTop,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Speaking of names, most of the guys who \Ncome to my place use such obvious aliases.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:02.15,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I wonder if Ono-san would use \Nsomething like "Amano-san."}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.65,DefaultTop,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Oh, man, I bet he does all kinds \Nof nasty stuff as Amano-san!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.89,DefaultTop,Ono,0,0,0,,{Could you two not turn my name into a joke?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:08.57,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's Amano-san who hits up the \Nsex workers first thing in the morning.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:09.97,DefaultTop,Ono,0,0,0,,{My name is Ono!}
